description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'Prenatal Cardio Workout [FAT BURN] Safe, No Equipment' from the channel GlowBodyPT.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
